'''前額葉皮質'''（{{lang|en|prefrontal cortex, PFC}}）位于[[大脑|大脑]][[额叶|额叶]]的前部、[[运动皮层|运动皮层]]和[[前运动区|前运动皮层]]的前方，包含[[布罗德曼分区系统|布罗德曼分区]]中的BA8、BA9、BA10、BA11、BA12、BA13、BA14、BA24、BA25、BA32、BA44、BA45、BA46，以及BA47区<ref name="PFC - list of 14 Brodmann areas">{{cite book|author1=Elisabeth Murray, Steven Wise, Kim Grahatle=The Evolution of Memory Systems: Ancestors, Anatomy, and Adaptations|title=The Evolution of Memory Systems: Ancestors, Anatomy, and Adaptations|date=2016|publisher=Oxford University Press|isbn=9780191509957|pages=22–24|edition=1st|chapter-url=https://books.google.com/books?id=eMNjDQAAQBAJ&pg=PA24&lpg=PA24|access-date=12 March 2017|chapter=Chapter 1: The History of Memory Systems|archive-date=2020-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200819061236/https://books.google.com/books?id=eMNjDQAAQBAJ&pg=PA24&lpg=PA24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

一般认为，前额叶皮质与人生存的欲望以及性格有关<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = DeYoung CG, Hirsh JB, Shane MS, Papademetris X, Rajeevan N, Gray JR | title = Testing predictions from personality neuroscience. Brain structure and the big five | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_psychological-science_2010-06_21_6/page/820 | journal = Psychological Science | volume = 21 | issue = 6 | pages = 820–8 | date = June 2010 | pmid = 20435951 | pmc = 3049165 | doi = 10.1177/0956797610370159 }}</ref>。具体来说，前额叶皮质涉及与计划相关的高层次认知活动、人格表现、作出决定的过程，以及调节社会活动、语言功能的某些方面等行为<ref name="pmid19833485">{{cite journal | vauthors = Yang Y, Raine A | title = Prefrontal structural and functional brain imaging findings in antisocial, violent, and psychopathic individuals: a meta-analysis | journal = Psychiatry Research | volume = 174 | issue = 2 | pages = 81–8 | date = November 2009 | pmid = 19833485 | pmc = 2784035 | doi = 10.1016/j.pscychresns.2009.03.012 }}</ref><ref name=":0">{{cite journal | vauthors = Gabrieli JD, Poldrack RA, Desmond JE | title = The role of left prefrontal cortex in language and memory | journal = Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the United States of America | volume = 95 | issue = 3 | pages = 906–13 | date = February 1998 | pmid = 9448258 | pmc = 33815 | doi = 10.1073/pnas.95.3.906 | bibcode = 1998PNAS...95..906G }}</ref>，能根据内在目标组织思考与行为<ref name="pmid12217179">{{cite journal | vauthors = Miller EK, Freedman DJ, Wallis JD | title = The prefrontal cortex: categories, concepts and cognition | journal = Philosophical Transactions of the Royal Society of London. Series B, Biological Sciences | volume = 357 | issue = 1424 | pages = 1123–36 | date = August 2002 | pmid = 12217179 | pmc = 1693009 | doi = 10.1098/rstb.2002.1099 }}</ref>。

按照[[细胞结构学|细胞结构学]]来讲，脑前额叶外皮通过第四层[[大脑皮质|大脑皮质]]而被定义存在。运动前区皮层可以通过几种方法来分，其中一种把它分为：[[前额脑区底部|前额脑区底部]]和{{le|腹內側前額葉皮質|ventromedial prefrontal cortex}}；{{le|背外側前額葉皮層|dorsolateral prefrontal cortex}}；[[前扣带皮层|前扣带皮层]]和[[后扣带皮层|后扣带皮层]]。

